creator: SwimKids LLC
descriptionHtml:
Get full access to your children’s swimming lessons for quickly reviewing and making changes to their scheduled lessons!


VIEW YOUR STUDENT’S LESSONS
Your student’s classes and attendance are right at your fingertips! No more wondering what time you scheduled your lessons, nor wondering when your child missed a class.


CANCEL & MAKEUP LESSONS
Need to miss a class? Submit future absences within the app to get the missed lesson’s makeup! Use your makeup tokens any time of day by signing your student up for a class. (Makeups don’t expire until 30 days after the missed lesson, and can be booked up to 7 days in advance)


BOOKING ON THE GO
Quickly find and register for the swimming lessons that are right for your student!


MOBILE NOTIFICATIONS
Stay in the know by enabling push notifications! Never miss an important announcement (or announced promotion) from SwimKids again!


ALL IN ONE DASHBOARD
With the SwimKids Dashboard, see when payments are due, and check out our engaging posts!
descriptionShort: Stay connected on the go with Swim Kids Utah for Android!

title: SwimKids Utah

descriptionHtml:
Get full access to your children’s swimming lessons for quickly reviewing and making changes to their scheduled lessons!


VIEW YOUR STUDENT’S LESSONS
Your student’s classes and attendance are right at your fingertips! No more wondering what time you scheduled your lessons, nor wondering when your child missed a class.


CANCEL & MAKEUP LESSONS
Need to miss a class? Submit future absences within the app to get the missed lesson’s makeup! Use your makeup tokens any time of day by signing your student up for a class. (Makeups don’t expire until 30 days after the missed lesson, and can be booked up to 7 days in advance)


BOOKING ON THE GO
Quickly find and register for the swimming lessons that are right for your student!


MOBILE NOTIFICATIONS
Stay in the know by enabling push notifications! Never miss an important announcement (or announced promotion) from SwimKids again!


ALL IN ONE DASHBOARD
With the SwimKids Dashboard, see when payments are due, and check out our engaging posts!
